  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK794">
<l>kuṭippiṟantu taṉkaṭ paḻināṇu vāṉaik</l>
<l>koṭuttuṅ koḷalvēṇṭu naṭpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The friendship of one who belongs to a (good) family and is afraid of (being charged with) guilt, is worth even purchasing.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
